HEADWORD: Practiced
<hw>Prac"ticed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Often written
<ets>practised</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Experienced; expert;
skilled; <as>as, a <ex>practiced</ex> marksman</as>.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A
<xex>practiced</xex> picklock.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Ld. Lytton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Used habitually; learned by practice.</def>⟦br⟧
